rows.label: qst00100103_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh! It's you! Thanks to
you, I was able to change
shifts with Rimurimu, mo!

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0002
rows.name:
He set a new lateness record,
surpassing his previous one
of 7691 seconds, mo...

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0003
rows.name:
Since this was his 1000th time being
late, I was planning to lecture him for
three days and three nights, but...

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0004
rows.name:
But Rimurimu gave Kebikebi
half of delicious Cinnopon
Roll, so Kebikebi forgive him.

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0005
rows.name:
My heart is wider than
the Cloud Sea, mo...

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0006
rows.name:
*yawn*... Eating that Nopopon
Roll made me sleepy, mo.

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0007
rows.name:
Please accept this reward from
the generous Kebikebi, mo.

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0008
rows.name:
If you see anyone suspicious
in Goldmund, report them to
Kebikebi or Rimurimu, mo!
